description: Try our easy to follow Cupcake Flowers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Cupcake,Seafood free,Sesame free,Quick & easy dessert,Peanut free
name: Cupcake Flowers Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Flatten out a small and a large paper muffin case and lay on top of a paper doily. Push a bamboo skewerthrough a marshmallow, then through the 3 paper layers and lastly into a Woolworths Mini Iced Cupcake (available in pk6, pk9 or pk24). Display flowers in jars or push skewers into polystyrene.
